{
  "type": "excalidraw",
  "version": 2,
  "source": "claude",
  "elements": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 900,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "Board memory budget + initial-board sources (back-fill for PR #6)",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "subtitle",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 80,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 40,
      "text": "--max-board-memory bounds InMemoryBoard allocations. --initial-board picks one of four built-in seeders.\nWhen the requested size exceeds the cap, the user gets a suggested override (and, since the streaming PR,\nthe initializer path auto-promotes to a StreamingBoard instead of failing).",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "cli_box",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 100,
      "strokeColor": "#1864ab",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "cli_label"}]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cli_label",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "CLI flags\n--max-board-memory <SIZE>\n--initial-board <SOURCE>\n--board-size <WxH>",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "cli_box"
    },
    {
      "type": "arrow",
      "id": "cli_to_config",
      "x": 325,
      "y": 210,
      "width": 60,
      "height": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "points": [[0, 0], [60, 0]],
      "startBinding": {"elementId": "cli_box", "focus": 0, "gap": 5},
      "endBinding": {"elementId": "config_box", "focus": 0, "gap": 5}
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "config_box",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 100,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "#dee2e6",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "config_label"}]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "config_label",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "SimulationConfig\nmax_board_memory_bytes: usize\ninitial_board: InitialBoardSpec\nboard_size: BoardSize",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "config_box"
    },
    {
      "type": "arrow",
      "id": "config_to_try_new",
      "x": 675,
      "y": 210,
      "width": 60,
      "height": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "points": [[0, 0], [60, 0]],
      "startBinding": {"elementId": "config_box", "focus": 0, "gap": 5},
      "endBinding": {"elementId": "try_new", "focus": 0, "gap": 5}
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "try_new",
      "x": 740,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 100,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "try_new_label"}]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "try_new_label",
      "x": 740,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "InMemoryBoard::try_new(w, h, max_bytes)\nallocation_bytes(w, h) =\n  w * h * size_of::<CellState>()\nreject if > max_bytes",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "try_new"
    },

    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "outcomes_title",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 290,
      "width": 1050,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "Three outcomes",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "outcome_ok",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 330,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 130,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "outcome_ok_label"}]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "outcome_ok_label",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 330,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "1. Fits\nAllocate Vec<CellState>;\nrun in memory normally.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "outcome_ok"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "outcome_overcap",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 330,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 130,
      "strokeColor": "#e67700",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "outcome_overcap_label"}]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "outcome_overcap_label",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 330,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "2. Exceeds --max-board-memory\nMemoryBudgetExceeded\nwith suggest_memory_override\n(e.g. 'try --max-board-memory 2MB')\n\nStreaming PR: --initial-board auto-\npromotes to StreamingBoard here.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "outcome_overcap"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "outcome_unreachable",
      "x": 760,
      "y": 330,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 130,
      "strokeColor": "#D13438",
      "backgroundColor": "#FDE7E9",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "outcome_unreachable_label"}]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "outcome_unreachable_label",
      "x": 760,
      "y": 330,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "3. Exceeds addressable memory\n(can't fit on this platform)\n\nAllocationAddressSpaceExceeded\n\nFuture remedy: streaming board\n(now shipped in the streaming PR).",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "outcome_unreachable"
    },

    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "init_title",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 500,
      "width": 1050,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "Initial-board source routing (--initial-board)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },

    {
